{"number":35,"verseCount":27,"verses":[[1,["Listen to the voice of the ",["Lord",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Lord","tg/jesus-christ-lord"],"."]]]," your God, even ",["Alpha and Omega",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rev. 1:8","nt/rev/1.8"],"; ",["D&C 19:1","dc-testament/dc/19.1"],"."]]],", the beginning and the end, whose ",["course",["study-note-ref","c",[["1 Ne. 10:19","bofm/1-ne/10.19"],"; ",["D&C 3:2","dc-testament/dc/3.2"],"."]]]," is one ",["eternal",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG God, Eternal Nature of","tg/god-eternal-nature-of"],"."]]]," round, the ",["same",["study-note-ref","e",[["Heb. 13:8","nt/heb/13.8"],"; ",["D&C 20:12","dc-testament/dc/20.12"],"; ",["38:1 (1–4)","dc-testament/dc/38.1"],"; ",["39:1 (1–3)","dc-testament/dc/39.1"],"; ",["76:4","dc-testament/dc/76.4"],"."]]]," today as yesterday, and forever."]],[2,["I am Jesus Christ, the Son of God, who was ",["crucified",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Crucifixion of","tg/jesus-christ-crucifixion-of"],"."]]]," for the sins of the world, even as many as will ",["believe",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 20:25","dc-testament/dc/20.25"],"; ",["38:4","dc-testament/dc/38.4"],"; ",["45:5 (5, 8)","dc-testament/dc/45.5"],"."]]]," on my name, that they may become the ",["sons",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Sons and Daughters of God","tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"],"."]]]," of God, even ",["one",["study-note-ref","d",[["John 17:21","nt/john/17.21"],"; ",["Moses 6:68","pgp/moses/6.68"],". ",["TG Unity","tg/unity"],"."]]]," in ",["me",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Jesus Christ, Exemplar","tg/jesus-christ-exemplar"],"."]]]," as I am ",["one",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Godhead","tg/godhead"],"."]]]," in the Father, as the Father is one in me, that we may be one."]],[3,["Behold, verily, verily, I say unto my servant Sidney, I have looked upon thee and thy works. I have ",["heard",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ex. 2:24 (23–24)","ot/ex/2.24"],"; ",["Mosiah 9:18 (17–18)","bofm/mosiah/9.18"],"; ",["Abr. 1:15 (15–16)","pgp/abr/1.15"],"."]]]," thy prayers, and prepared thee for a greater work."]],[4,["Thou art blessed, for thou shalt do great things. Behold thou wast sent forth, even as ",["John",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mal. 3:1","ot/mal/3.1"],"; ",["Matt. 11:10","nt/matt/11.10"],"; ",["John 5:33","nt/john/5.33"],"; ",["1 Ne. 11:27","bofm/1-ne/11.27"],"; ",["D&C 84:27 (27–28)","dc-testament/dc/84.27"],"."]]],", to prepare the way before me, and before ",["Elijah",["study-note-ref","b",[["3 Ne. 25:5 (5–6)","bofm/3-ne/25.5"],"; ",["D&C 2:1","dc-testament/dc/2.1"],"; ",["110:13 (13–15)","dc-testament/dc/110.13"],"; ",["128:17","dc-testament/dc/128.17"],"."]]]," which should come, and thou knewest it not."]],[5,["Thou didst baptize by water unto repentance, but they ",["received not",["study-note-ref","a",[["Acts 19:2 (1–6)","nt/acts/19.2"],"."]]]," the Holy Ghost;"]],[6,["But now I give unto thee a commandment, that thou shalt ",["baptize",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Baptism","tg/baptism"],"."]]]," by water, and they shall receive the ",["Holy Ghost",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Holy Ghost, Gift of","tg/holy-ghost-gift-of"],"."]]]," by the laying on ",["",60],"of the ",["hands",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Hands, Laying on of","tg/hands-laying-on-of"],"."]]],", even as the apostles of old."]],[7,["And it shall come to pass that there shall be a great work in the land, even among the ",["Gentiles",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 66:12","ot/isa/66.12"],". ",["TG Gentiles","tg/gentiles"],"."]]],", for their ",["folly",["study-note-ref","b",[["Eccl. 10:12 (1–3, 12)","ot/eccl/10.12"],"; ",["2 Tim. 3:9","nt/2-tim/3.9"],"; ",["2 Ne. 9:28 (28–29)","bofm/2-ne/9.28"],"; ",["19:17","bofm/2-ne/19.17"],"."]]]," and their abominations shall be made manifest in the eyes of all people."]],[8,["For I am God, and mine arm is not ",["shortened",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 50:2 (2–4)","ot/isa/50.2"],"; ",["59:1","ot/isa/59.1"],"."]]],"; and I will show ",["miracles",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Miracle","tg/miracle"],"."]]],", ",["signs",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Signs","tg/signs"],"."]]],", and wonders, unto all those who ",["believe",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Believe","tg/believe"],"; ",["Trust in God","tg/trust-in-god"],"."]]]," on my name."]],[9,["And whoso shall ask it in my name in ",["faith",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Faith","tg/faith"],"."]]],", they shall ",["cast out",["study-note-ref","b",[["Mark 16:17","nt/mark/16.17"],"."]]]," ",["devils",["study-note-ref","c",[["Mark 1:39 (21–45)","nt/mark/1.39"],"."]]],"; they shall heal the ",["sick",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Heal","tg/heal"],"; ",["Sickness","tg/sickness"],"."]]],"; they shall cause the blind to receive their ",["sight",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Sight","tg/sight"],"."]]],", and the deaf to hear, and the dumb to speak, and the lame to walk."]],[10,["And the time ",["speedily",["study-note-ref","a",[["JS—H 1:41","pgp/js-h/1.41"],"."]]]," cometh that great things are to be shown forth unto the children of men;"]],[11,["But ",["without faith",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 63:11 (7–12)","dc-testament/dc/63.11"],"."]]]," shall not anything be shown forth except ",["desolations",["study-note-ref","b",[["Jer. 51:62","ot/jer/51.62"],"; ",["D&C 5:19 (19–20)","dc-testament/dc/5.19"],"; ",["29:8","dc-testament/dc/29.8"],"; ",["43:17 (17–27)","dc-testament/dc/43.17"],"."]]]," upon ",["Babylon",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Babylon","tg/babylon"],"."]]],", the same which has made ",["all",["study-note-ref","d",[["1 Ne. 14:11 (10–13)","bofm/1-ne/14.11"],"."]]]," nations drink of the wine of the wrath of her ",["fornication",["study-note-ref","e",[["Rev. 18:3","nt/rev/18.3"],"."]]],"."]],[12,["And there are ",["none",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rom. 3:12","nt/rom/3.12"],"; ",["Moro. 7:13 (12–13)","bofm/moro/7.13"],"; ",["D&C 33:4","dc-testament/dc/33.4"],"; ",["38:11","dc-testament/dc/38.11"],"; ",["84:47 (47–51)","dc-testament/dc/84.47"],"."]]]," that doeth good except those who are ready to ",["receive",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Missionary Work","tg/missionary-work"],"; ",["Teachable","tg/teachable"],"."]]]," the fulness of my gospel, which I have sent forth unto this generation."]],[13,["Wherefore, I call upon the ",["weak",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Cor. 1:27","nt/1-cor/1.27"],"; ",["D&C 1:19 (19, 23)","dc-testament/dc/1.19"],"; ",["124:1","dc-testament/dc/124.1"],"."]]]," things of the world, those who are ",["unlearned",["study-note-ref","b",[["Acts 4:13","nt/acts/4.13"],"."]]]," and despised, to thresh the ",["nations",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Nations","tg/nations"],"."]]]," by the power of my ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG God, Spirit of","tg/god-spirit-of"],"."]]],";"]],[14,["And their arm shall be my arm, and I will be their ",["shield",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Sam. 22:3","ot/2-sam/22.3"],"; ",["Ps. 33:20","ot/ps/33.20"],"; ",["91:4","ot/ps/91.4"],"."]]]," and their buckler; and I will gird up their loins, and they shall fight manfully for me; and their ",["enemies",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 98:37 (34–38)","dc-testament/dc/98.37"],"."]]]," shall be under their feet; and I will let ",["fall",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 1:14 (13–14)","dc-testament/dc/1.14"],"; ",["45:47","dc-testament/dc/45.47"],"."]]]," the ",["sword",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 1:13","dc-testament/dc/1.13"],"."]]]," in their behalf, and by the ",["fire",["study-note-ref","e",[["Num. 11:1 (1, 10)","ot/num/11.1"],"; ",["D&C 128:24","dc-testament/dc/128.24"],"; ",["Moses 7:34","pgp/moses/7.34"],"."]]]," of mine indignation will I preserve them."]],[15,["And the ",["poor",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 11:5","nt/matt/11.5"],"."]]]," and the ",["meek",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Meek","tg/meek"],"."]]]," shall have the gospel preached unto them, and they shall be ",["looking",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Pet. 3:12 (10–13)","nt/2-pet/3.12"],"; ",["D&C 39:23","dc-testament/dc/39.23"],"; ",["45:39","dc-testament/dc/45.39"],"; ",["Moses 7:62","pgp/moses/7.62"],"."]]]," forth for the time of my coming, for it is ",["nigh",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 63:53","dc-testament/dc/63.53"],"."]]]," at hand—"]],[16,["And they shall learn the parable of the ",["fig tree",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 24:32","nt/matt/24.32"],"; ",["Luke 21:29 (29–30)","nt/luke/21.29"],"; ",["D&C 45:37 (36–38)","dc-testament/dc/45.37"],"; ",["JS—M 1:38","pgp/js-m/1.38"],". ",["TG Last Days","tg/last-days"],"."]]],", for even now already summer is nigh."]],[17,["And I have sent forth the ",["fulness",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rom. 15:29","nt/rom/15.29"],"; ",["D&C 42:12","dc-testament/dc/42.12"],"; ",["135:3","dc-testament/dc/135.3"],"."]]]," of my gospel by the hand of my servant Joseph; and in weakness have I blessed him;"]],[18,["And I have given unto him the ",["keys",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 28:7","dc-testament/dc/28.7"],"; ",["84:19","dc-testament/dc/84.19"],"."]]]," of the mystery of those things which have been ",["sealed",["study-note-ref","b",[["Dan. 12:9","ot/dan/12.9"],"; ",["Matt. 13:35","nt/matt/13.35"],"; ",["1 Ne. 14:26","bofm/1-ne/14.26"],"; ",["2 Ne. 27:10","bofm/2-ne/27.10"],"; ",["Ether 4:5 (4–7)","bofm/ether/4.5"],"; ",["JS—H 1:65","pgp/js-h/1.65"],"."]]],", even things which were from the ",["foundation",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 128:18","dc-testament/dc/128.18"],"."]]]," of the world, and the things which shall come from this time until the time of my coming, if he ",["abide",["study-note-ref","d",[["John 15:4 (4, 7)","nt/john/15.4"],"."]]]," in me, and if not, ",["another",["study-note-ref","e",[["D&C 42:10","dc-testament/dc/42.10"],"; ",["64:40","dc-testament/dc/64.40"],"; ",["104:77","dc-testament/dc/104.77"],"; ",["107:99 (99–100)","dc-testament/dc/107.99"],"."]]]," will I plant in his stead."]],[19,["Wherefore, watch over him ",["",61],"that his faith fail not, and it shall be given by the ",["Comforter",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 14:16, 26","nt/john/14.16,26"],"; ",["15:26","nt/john/15.26"],"; ",["1 Cor. 12:8","nt/1-cor/12.8"],"."]]],", the ",["Holy Ghost",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Cor. 2:10","nt/1-cor/2.10"],"."]]],", that knoweth all things."]],[20,["And a commandment I give unto thee—that thou shalt ",["write",["study-note-ref","a",["The Prophet was at this time engaged in a revelatory translation of the Bible, to which Sidney Rigdon was called as scribe."]]]," for him; and the ",["scriptures",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 6:27","dc-testament/dc/6.27"],"; ",["37:1","dc-testament/dc/37.1"],"; ",["42:15 (15, 56–58)","dc-testament/dc/42.15"],"."]]]," shall be given, even as they are in mine own bosom, to the salvation of mine own ",["elect",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Election","tg/election"],"."]]],";"]],[21,["For they will hear my ",["voice",["study-note-ref","a",[["Joel 2:11","ot/joel/2.11"],"; ",["John 10:3","nt/john/10.3"],"; ",["D&C 43:18 (17–25)","dc-testament/dc/43.18"],"; ",["88:90","dc-testament/dc/88.90"],"; ",["133:50 (50–52)","dc-testament/dc/133.50"],"."]]],", and shall ",["see",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 16:16","nt/john/16.16"],". ",["TG God, Privilege of Seeing","tg/god-privilege-of-seeing"],"."]]]," me, and shall not be ",["asleep",["study-note-ref","c",[["Matt. 25:5","nt/matt/25.5"],"."]]],", and shall ",["abide",["study-note-ref","d",[["Mal. 3:2","ot/mal/3.2"],"."]]]," the day of my ",["coming",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Jesus Christ, Prophecies about","tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Second Coming","tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"],"."]]],"; for they shall be ",["purified",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Purification","tg/purification"],"."]]],", even as I am pure."]],[22,["And now I say unto you, ",["tarry",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 90:6","dc-testament/dc/90.6"],"; ",["100:9 (9–11)","dc-testament/dc/100.9"],"."]]]," with him, and he shall journey with you; forsake him not, and surely these things shall be fulfilled."]],[23,["And ",["inasmuch",["study-note-ref","a",["IE whenever you are not occupied with writing."]]]," as ye do not write, behold, it shall be ",["given",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Cor. 12:8","nt/1-cor/12.8"],"."]]]," unto him to prophesy; and thou shalt preach my gospel and call on ",["the holy prophets",["study-note-ref","c",["IE the scriptures."]]]," to prove his words, as they shall be given him."]],[24,[["Keep",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 66:11","dc-testament/dc/66.11"],"; ",["103:7","dc-testament/dc/103.7"],"."]]]," all the commandments and covenants by which ye are bound; and I will cause the heavens to ",["shake",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 21:6","dc-testament/dc/21.6"],"."]]]," for your ",["good",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Blessing","tg/blessing"],"."]]],", and ",["Satan",["study-note-ref","d",[["1 Ne. 22:26","bofm/1-ne/22.26"],"; ",["Alma 48:17","bofm/alma/48.17"],"."]]]," shall tremble and ",["Zion",["study-note-ref","e",[["D&C 6:6","dc-testament/dc/6.6"],"."]]]," shall ",["rejoice",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Joy","tg/joy"],"."]]]," upon the hills and ",["flourish",["study-note-ref","g",[["D&C 39:13","dc-testament/dc/39.13"],"; ",["49:25","dc-testament/dc/49.25"],"; ",["117:7 (7–8)","dc-testament/dc/117.7"],"."]]],";"]],[25,["And ",["Israel",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Israel, Blessings of","tg/israel-blessings-of"],"; ",["Israel, Restoration of","tg/israel-restoration-of"],"; ",["Israel, Ten Lost Tribes of","tg/israel-ten-lost-tribes-of"],"; ",["Israel, Twelve Tribes of","tg/israel-twelve-tribes-of"],"."]]]," shall be ",["saved",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ps. 94:14","ot/ps/94.14"],"; ",["Isa. 45:17","ot/isa/45.17"],"; ",["1 Ne. 19:16 (15–16)","bofm/1-ne/19.16"],"; ",["22:12","bofm/1-ne/22.12"],". ",["TG Israel, Deliverance of","tg/israel-deliverance-of"],"."]]]," in mine own due time; and by the ",["keys",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Priesthood, Keys of","tg/priesthood-keys-of"],"."]]]," which I have given shall they be led, and no more be confounded at all."]],[26,[["Lift",["study-note-ref","a",[["Lam. 3:41","ot/lam/3.41"],"."]]]," up your hearts and be glad, your ",["redemption",["study-note-ref","b",[["Luke 21:28","nt/luke/21.28"],"; ",["Rom. 13:11","nt/rom/13.11"],"."]]]," draweth nigh."]],[27,["Fear not, little ",["flock",["study-note-ref","a",[["Luke 12:32","nt/luke/12.32"],". ",["TG Church","tg/church"],"; ",["Sheep","tg/sheep"],"."]]],", the ",["kingdom",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 29:5","dc-testament/dc/29.5"],"; ",["38:9","dc-testament/dc/38.9"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming","tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"],"; ",["Kingdom of God, on Earth","tg/kingdom-of-god-on-earth"],"."]]]," is yours until I come. Behold, I ",["come",["study-note-ref","c",[["Rev. 22:20","nt/rev/22.20"],"."]]]," quickly. Even so. Amen."]]],"volume":"dc"}